704083f-a.title: Brooklyn: Elm Place - Livingston Street
704083f-a.text:
Elm Place, north from Livingston to Fulton Streets,
showing, on the latter, the B. M. T. Elm Street station.
The street is a short, one-block thoroughfare.
April 27, 1940
P. L. Sperr
